“The sea is ours”: Bolivia, blocked, hopes the court will reopen the way to the Pacific
Marines are patrolling in an armored boat at Naval Headquarters La Paz.
Public buildings carry a blue flag like the ocean.
From Lake Titicaca to the Amazon, the naval bases display the following motorcycle: “The sea is rightfully ours.
